AUDIO: 'Right here, this is a forward-facing lidar sensor, and it\'s the headline feature of the X1 over the base Lito 1. Now, most drones at this price rely purely on cameras to detect obstacles. The Lito X1 pairs its'

[03:23] [scene:talk]
